cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.HC 

The paper deals with visual object tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves motion patterns, which are related to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM). The evaluation system and dataset creation involve graphics (cs.GR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
